@startuml Plant Seasonal Lifecycle

state Winter 
state Spring
state Summer
state Autumn

[*] --> Winter
Winter --> Spring : TemperatureRises
Spring --> Summer : DaylightIncreases \ StartBlooming
Summer --> Autumn : DaylightDecreases \ RipenFruit
Autumn --> Winter : TemperatureDrops  \ DropPetals 

@endumld
